{"lastModified":1773243809253,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::fe7f5df0-1f9a-11f0-9422-392af2a6e72f","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nWelcoming the Brand-New Oceanis 60 Scorpio III to the MK Fleet!\n\nWe’re proud to introduce the luxurious Oceanis 60 Scorpio III, the latest addition to the MK Yacht Explorer Fleet, now available for now available for crewed charters from Marina Baotić, Croatia. This brand-new, state-of-the-art yacht is the epitome of comfort and performance, offering a premium sailing experience for discerning sailors.\n\nThe 3-cabin owner version of the Oceanis 60 features spacious, elegantly designed interiors with high-end finishes, ensuring a luxurious stay for up to 6 guests. Equipped with air conditioning, a generator, and the latest navigation and safety systems, Scorpio III is perfect for exploring the Adriatic in both style and confidence. Its expansive cockpit and sunbathing areas provide ample space for relaxation, while its innovative sail plan ensures easy handling and exceptional performance.\n\nWhy book this yacht?\n\n• Unmatched luxury: A perfect choice for those seeking high-end comfort on the water.\n• Fully equipped: Includes AC, generator, and modern technology for a seamless charter experience.\n• Prime location: Based in Marina Baotić, near Trogir, a gateway to Croatia’s most beautiful islands and coastline.\n• Exclusive offering: The latest model in the Oceanis range, delivering the ultimate in style and functionality.\n\nExperience the pinnacle of sailing aboard Scorpio III. Your Adriatic adventure begins with MK Yacht Explorer!","blueprint":{"name":"SCORPIO III","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe7f5df0-1f9a-11f0-9422-392af2a6e72f::assets::3b799a70-1fa7-11f0-ac08-d38826b03cbd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe7f5df0-1f9a-11f0-9422-392af2a6e72f::assets::dac88000-c9fc-11f0-b528-8b671d0c52f3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::fe7f5df0-1f9a-11f0-9422-392af2a6